: \(X_1, \ldots, X_{n_1} \sim iid \hspace{2mm} Bern(p)\) \(Y_1, \ldots, Y_{n_2} \sim iid \hspace{2mm} Bern(p)\)

:

\[ \begin{aligned} &H_0: \hspace{2mm} p_1 = p_2 \\ &H_1: \hspace{2mm} p_1 < \ne > p_2 \end{aligned} \]

:

\[ \begin{aligned} \hat{p}_1 &\sim N\left(p, \frac{p(1-p)}{n_1} \right) \\ \hat{p}_2 &\sim N\left(p, \frac{p(1-p)}{n_2} \right) \end{aligned} \]

\(Z\)-

:

\[ Z = \frac{\hat p_1 - \hat p_2}{\sqrt{P(1-P)\frac{n_1 + n_2}{n_1 n_2}}} \sim N(0,1), \]

\[P = \frac{m_1 + m_2}{n_1 + n_2} = \frac{\hat p_1 n_1 + \hat p_2 n_2}{n_1 + n_2}\]
